{"tid":2070583,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"弗洛伊德弟弟促聯國調查美國警暴　望糾正種族歧視 人權事務高級專員贊同要正視種族歧視問題，並指黑人的性命也很重要","createTime":"2020-06-19T08:23:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T10:21:27.000Z","uid":133680,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"00617de9076f50747ca95a998e9e9d043de2c5c1","tid":2070583,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T08:23:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20200618/bkn-20200618220131089-0618_00972_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20200618%2Fbkn-20200618220131089-0618_00972_001.html&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84C8bSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=9ffbd24d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20200618/bkn-20200618220131089-0618_00972_001.html</a><br />\n美國黑人弗洛伊德上月底遭白人警跪頸致死，引發全球反種族歧視示威。其弟弟菲隆尼斯（Philonise Floyd）周三（17日）在聯合國人權理事會的緊急辯論上，懇請聯合國着手調查美國警暴及種族問題。<br />\n是次緊急辯論由54個非洲成員國提出，他們於周二（16日）提交決議草案，呼籲成立調查委員會，調查美國非裔黑人因濫暴致死的問題。菲隆尼斯翌日於透過視像形式向瑞士日内瓦的人權理事會發言，要求理事會展開高級別調查。他情緒激動地說：「我求你們（理事會）幫他（弗洛伊德）。我求你們幫我。我求你們幫助我們&mdash;&mdash;美國黑人。」<br />\n人權事務高級專員巴切萊特（Michelle Bachelet）其後亦表示贊同要正視種族歧視問題，並指黑人及原住民的性命也很重要。惟美方指控成員國虛偽及充滿偏見，於2年前已退出人權理事會，因而未有參與是次緊急辯論。緊急辯論將於周四（18日）繼續，屆時可能會為事件提出動議並投票"},{"pid":"dd6cfc33b52a87d24cec47eaa8598b03bb72c4a4","tid":2070583,"uid":121146,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T08:28:01.000Z","msg":"反智既世界"},{"pid":"65ed98bca0fe8c9f4e8c726a1c7cd42f02b340ac","tid":2070583,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd6cfc33b52a87d24cec47eaa8598b03bb72c4a4","tid":2070583,"uid":121146,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T08:28:01.000Z","msg":"反智既世界"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T08:33:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pRyWy0B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpRyWy0B.png&h=0c29556b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AG1Jd0C.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAG1Jd0C.png&h=de2fa764&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jkFxRNi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjkFxRNi.jpg&h=1dc41041&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"25e682e6288a5cedd1c859504a36276fb8cb1740","tid":2070583,"uid":235152,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T09:05:43.000Z","msg":"中國霸凌其他國家地區,我睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4267d53325a6bc7e20981d11ccf882b30a50ddf","tid":2070583,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T09:54:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abd3fcaa0856d2c73aa88e07415a90d37b8bf3af","tid":2070583,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T10:11:06.000Z","msg":"朋友，不如你返非洲喇，個個都係黑色肯定冇歧視喇"},{"pid":"2e0027f000b5621cebde67bc466695bdf1077fc4","tid":2070583,"uid":138964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"25e682e6288a5cedd1c859504a36276fb8cb1740","tid":2070583,"uid":235152,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T09:05:43.000Z","msg":"中國霸凌其他國家地區,我睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T10:21:27.000Z","msg":"咁巧合又會發大到咁規模 <br />\n發展到全世界<br />\n<br />\n香港咁大件事就國際組織就盲左<br />\n<br />\n改革美國警察都平息唔到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}